          <title>
            <string language="en">Canon/Piano Quartet No.1 Barry</string>
            <string language="es">Cuarteto Barry nº 1 para Canon/Piano</string>
            <string language="ga">Canon/Piano Quartet No.1 Barry</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Canon/Piano Quartett No.1 Barry</string>

          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This is an exercise examining canonic writing in the Barry Quartet. You are invited to apply the principles discovered to their composition.</string>
            <string language="es">Este es un ejercicio que examina la escritura canónica en el cuarteto de Barry. Se invita a aplicar los principios descubiertos a la composición propia.</string>
            <string language="ga">Is ceacht é seo a scrúdaíonn scríbhneoireacht canonic sa Barry Quartet. Tugtar cuireadh duit prionsabail a fhaigheann tu a chur i bhfeidhm ar a saothair.</string>
          </description>
          <language>en</language>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Music</string>
            <string language="es">Música. Hoja de trabajo</string>
            <string language="ga">Ceol</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Worksheet</string>
            <string language="ga">Bileog Oibre</string>
          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Dieses ist eine Übung, die canonic Schreiben im 
Barry Quartett überprüft. Sie werden eingeladen, die 
Grundregeln anzuwenden, die an ihrem Aufbau entdeckt werden.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">C'est un exercice examinant l'écriture 
canoniale dans le quartet de Barry. Vous êtes invité à vous
appliquer les principes découverts à leur composition.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Este é um exercício que examina a escrita 
canonic no quartet de Barry. Você é convidado aplicar os 
princípios descobertos a sua composição.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Ciò è un'esercitazione che esamina la scrittura
canonic nel Quartetto di Barry. Siete invitati ad applicare i 
principii scoperti alla loro composizione.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτό είναι μια άσκηση που εξετάζει το κανονικό 
γράψιμο στο Κουαρτέτο του Barry. Καλείστε για να 
εφαρμόσετε τις αρχές που ανακαλύπτονται στη σύνθεσή τους.</string>
          </description>
